{"tid":2399074,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"將兩款武肺疫苗各打一劑，是否可行？","createTime":"2021-02-07T21:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T07:37:27.000Z","uid":38861,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e68801b52b5186fca395573e1429ab23f4142da6","tid":2399074,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:25:44.000Z","msg":"現今不少的武肺疫苗在打上第一劑後，隔一段時間後便需打上第二劑，用意是希望增強身體的免疫系統反應，訓練免疫系統細胞記認武肺病毒的組件。<br />\n<br />\n情形就像是強迫免疫細胞重覆溫習課本，當考試（武肺病毒）來臨的時候，免疫細胞亦懂得妥善應對。<br />\n<br />\n 而我們身體對抗武肺病毒的手段，大致上可分成為兩種。<br />\n<br />\n第一種手段就是在體內產生具中和性的抗體，當具中和性的抗體與病毒結合後，一來可以阻止病毒入侵身體細胞，二來亦可幫忙標示病毒的存在，讓某類別的免疫細胞前來消滅病毒。<br />\n<br />\n而第二種手段，就是摧毀已被病毒感染的細胞，這工作交由對應武肺病毒的CD8+T免疫細胞負責。<br />\n<br />\n「有趣」的是，現今的mRNA疫苗（Moderna以及輝瑞），在協助身體製作抗體（第一種手段）方面，相對上較為優勝於牛津疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n但是，在催谷身體生產對應武肺病毒的CD8+T免疫細胞（第二種手段）方面，牛津疫苗卻比mRNA疫苗優勝。<br />\n<br />\n至於中國製的疫苗，因為至今尚未有明確的數據，暫時略為難以比較。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，基於mRNA疫苗及牛津疫苗在應對武肺病毒方面各有千秋，不其然便會讓人生起兩者各打一劑是否會效果更好的念頭。<br />\n<br />\n有科學家嘗試在老鼠身上作實驗，分別比較兩劑RNA疫苗、兩劑牛津疫苗、一劑RNA一劑牛津疫苗的成效，兩劑相隔的時間為4星期。<br />\n<br />\n報告在1月29日率先刊登在未經學術同輩審查的期刊上（Ref1），得出的結果是，注射一劑RNA一劑牛津疫苗的老鼠體內，其抗體（第一種手段）及CD8+T免疫細胞（第二種手段）含量均比另外兩種組別為高。<br />\n<br />\n大概是建基於這研究結果，牛津大學宣佈在2月4日起招募820人進行一劑輝瑞mRNA疫苗及一劑牛津疫苗的人體測試，一組人將會相隔4星期注射第二劑，另一組人則相隔12星期注射。<br />\n<br />\n研究目的是希望檢驗這方法的安全性，以及體外產生抗體和CD8+T免疫細胞的效率，預期會在六月公佈結果。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2021.01.28.428665v1.full.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biorxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2021.01.28.428665v1.full.pdf&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUinwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=70fd5519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2021.01.28.428665v1.full.pdf</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-021-00315-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-021-00315-5&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUinwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=a5ddef60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-021-00315-5</a>"},{"pid":"ead337e44bc5d30d7b4b45ecc97d6f01e71719e2","tid":2399074,"uid":38861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:27:45.000Z","msg":"研究目的是希望檢驗這方法的安全性，以及<span class=\"red\">體內</span>產生抗體和CD8+T免疫細胞的效率，預期會在六月公佈結果。"},{"pid":"252efb701df2fbea232a73302b5e807f707f0408","tid":2399074,"uid":85461,"like":8,"dislike":15,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:29:24.000Z","msg":"別吵了 做尿尿牛肉丸就行了 笨！"},{"pid":"aac051df2f5c02f37d06fd03189f8bb7b8b985f2","tid":2399074,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"252efb701df2fbea232a73302b5e807f707f0408","tid":2399074,"uid":85461,"like":8,"dislike":15,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:29:24.000Z","msg":"別吵了 做尿尿牛肉丸就行了 笨！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:35:31.000Z","msg":"瀨尿蝦牛丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3706f6feedafa6cb3f2c70a1d962c711c3ed1c","tid":2399074,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:44:06.000Z","msg":"所以可行唔可行?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dcc408ca2736068a567edc418b796538c9dd9b","tid":2399074,"uid":255980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:57:42.000Z","msg":"最弊而家製造唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a52a6a4fd15692627898ef4bb1c32770792449","tid":2399074,"uid":253608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T22:05:34.000Z","msg":"咁溝法怕唔怕會有ADE<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f97183c7437c3ed312a04ef2cc967d73b925e1","tid":2399074,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f3706f6feedafa6cb3f2c70a1d962c711c3ed1c","tid":2399074,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:44:06.000Z","msg":"所以可行唔可行?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T23:17:04.000Z","msg":"研究中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42840b30e5221c76a1ca2e7152a5156db5c84742","tid":2399074,"uid":11185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T23:29:18.000Z","msg":"一杯凍鴦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa717a23c11fd8c84b17d1026e4e51327c90d3b1","tid":2399074,"uid":251736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T23:48:46.000Z","msg":"至於中國製的疫苗，因為至今尚未有明確的數據，暫時略為難以比較。<br />\n<br />\n樓主已犯國安法"},{"pid":"fe06e03462079d717916224d38fbf5df0373ee8b","tid":2399074,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c44b81fa4a4791a4d4d074a981827965f679937","tid":2399074,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T04:40:25.000Z","msg":"如果要投票淨係揀一種 我會投RNA 因為一開始就入侵唔到細胞好似係最理想方法 當然你之前有講過ADE"},{"pid":"144eb1d90286f150f1ca49507b22a1eb710c2c02","tid":2399074,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5a52a6a4fd15692627898ef4bb1c32770792449","tid":2399074,"uid":253608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T22:05:34.000Z","msg":"咁溝法怕唔怕會有ADE<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"應該就唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38565d518b82fa77e45b6ad172638a611c79b72","tid":2399074,"uid":5220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:24:05.000Z","msg":"之前英國俾人兩溝打疫苗俾人笑<br />\n原來英國咁深謀遠慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124dc90198830cabb427313cc30365ed21b68e1b","tid":2399074,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited